# By_b[(n,m)] = [(c, p, q, k), ...]  means  By += c * h^k * x^p * y^q * b(n,m)
# Similarly for Bx_b, Bs_b, By_a, Bx_a, Bs_a, By_bs, Bx_bs, Bs_bs.
# Notation: b(n,m) = d^m b_n/ds^m,  a(n,m) = d^m a_n/ds^m,
#           bs(m)  = d^{m+1} a_0/ds^{m+1}

